'''Anita Pendo'''  ni [[Rwanda|Umunyarwandakazi]] wavukiye muri [[Ubugande|Uganda]] muri 1986 , ni umunyamakuru wa [https://www.rba.co.rw/ RBA.]

== Umwuga ==
Anita ni umunyamakuru kuri [https://www.rba.co.rw/ RBA], akaba akora nka  Mc aribyo umushyushyarugamba, DJ aribyo kuvanga imiziki, ikinamico,umubyinnyi  aramamaza ndetse no gushabika.[https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/109007#:~:text=Pendo%20was%20born%20in%20February,also%20stayed%20with%20her%20grandmother] 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Anita yavuste 1986 muri  Mengo, Uganda, niho yabaga numuryango we. Mukwezi kwa munani 1994 nibwo we numuryango we bagarutse mu Rwanda. Anita numwana wambere mubana barindwi, bavutse kubabyeyi aribo  Syprien Mpabuka na Apophia Mukampabuka. Yize gufata inshingano mu gihe yabuze umubyeyi we wumugabo akiri muto, yarezwe na Mama we ariko aba kwa Nyirakuru.  Anita ni umunyamuhate ndetse n umunyambaraga.[https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/109007#:~:text=Pendo%20was%20born%20in%20February,also%20stayed%20with%20her%20grandmother]

